  Locus:
    Page: 74
    Verse: 13
Tags:
  - Death
---
Death as the termination of life is the greatest lie which has been perpetrated
upon mankind. For the truth is that it is quite impossible to kill YOU. Only
the body can die. The real YOU, as an individual consciousness which dwells
within that body, is entirely beyond death.
